- cs.DM (Combinatorics) is another possible category as the paper deals with the construction of complementary dual codes.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve computational complexity analysis of the codes.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also less likely but possible as the paper may have applications in cryptography and security.
